---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Accordion from '../components/Accordion.astro'
import AccordionItem from '../components/AccordionItem.astro'
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import BreadcrumbsItem from '../components/BreadcrumbsItem.astro'
import Icon from '../components/Icon.astro'
---

<Layout title="agenda">
<body>
<Breadcrumbs>
  <BreadcrumbsItem
    href="/"
    label="Home"
  />
  <BreadcrumbsItem
    currentPage={true}
    label="Agenda"
  />
</Breadcrumbs>

<h2 class="title">Agenda</h2>


<Accordion>


  <AccordionItem
    header="Introduction"
  >
    <p>Who; Why; What; Where;</p>
  </AccordionItem>
  <AccordionItem
    header="Obsidian Zettelkasten / Personal Knowledge Management"
  >
    <ol>
          <li>
            <p>What is this and why would i want to use it?</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Download this <a href="https://github.com/ATH42/obsidian-seminar.git">repo</a></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Repo Walkthrough</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Create some templates</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Utilize created Templates in your first daily note</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>consolidate info from daily notes into MOC's and weekly notes</p>
          </li>
    </ol>
  </AccordionItem>

  <AccordionItem
    header="Vim Motions"
  >
    <ol>
          <li>
            <p>What the frick is vim? and why whould i use it over VScode?</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>Vimtutor or <a href="https://www.vim-hero.com/">Vimhero</a></p>
          </li>
    </ol>
  </AccordionItem>

  <AccordionItem
    header="Shell and Terminal Emu's"
  >
    <ol>
          <li>
            <pre>
        <code>
    defaults write -g InitialKeyRepeat -int 15 
    defaults write -g KeyRepeat -int 1 
    
    defaults write com.apple.dock autohide-delay -float 0; killall Dock
        </code>
</pre>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>intro into dotfiles</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>What is a shell?</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>What is a terminal emulator?</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><a href="https://tiswww.case.edu/php/chet/bash/bashtop.html">bash</a> / <a href="https://zsh.sourceforge.io/">zsh</a>/ <a href="https://fishshell.com/">fish</a></p>
          </li>
            <li>
              <p><a href="https://ohmyz.sh/">oh-my-zsh</a> / <a href="https://github.com/oh-my-fish/oh-my-fish">oh-my-fish</a> & <a href="https://github.com/jorgebucaran/fisher">fisher</a></p>
            </li>
          <li>
            <p>aliasing different commands</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>useful CLI's that i use every day</p>
            <ul>
              <li>z</li>
              <li>exa</li>
              <li>bat</li>
              <li>lazygit</li>
          </li>
    </ol>

  </AccordionItem>
  <AccordionItem
    header="Overall Workspace & Raycast"
  >
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Architecto quasi nobis optio? Qui in quo accusantium debitis sapiente obcaecati magnam incidunt sit. Molestiae exercitationem quibusdam quod veritatis laboriosam est tenetur. </p>
  </AccordionItem>
</Accordion>

<Icon icon="smooth-line" />
</body>
</Layout>

<style>

	body {
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 100vw;
		font-size: 20px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: white;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}

.title {
    font-size: 5em;
    background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 300%;
		background-position: 0%;

}
</style>
